text: Burhelmes boc a on ece erfe.
Of deonflinc forda in holan bæce.
Of ymman holigne in cudan dene.
Of cudan dene on ða ðic bufan foxcotun andlang dices to þam broce to þam stangedelfe.
Of tham stangedelfe be þære efese to wala crofte.
Of wala crofte in þone suðeran holan bæce.
Of stancofan andlong dune on stiran mere.
Of stiran mere on þa strete.
Andlong stræte on þa stapelas of þan stapulum on windofer of windofere in acleg.
Of aclea to lusdune of lusdune on sican byrig.
Et long stræte to meredic of mæredice on sture.
